{"result": {"folders": ["lab7"], "nr": 397, "data": {"embed_links": []}, "created": "2015-05-07T07:17:45Z", "bucket_order": 3, "no_answer_followup": 0, "change_log": [{"uid": "i6roqnlkmtw", "anon": "no", "when": "2015-05-07T07:17:45Z", "data": "i9dudbt8g8j263", "type": "create"}, {"to": "i9dudbt5alg262", "uid": "hxu22d7okof4c1", "anon": "no", "when": "2015-05-07T07:41:15Z", "data": "i9dv7k4zlvoie", "type": "s_answer"}, {"to": "i9dudbt5alg262", "uid": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "anon": "no", "when": "2015-05-07T07:47:13Z", "data": "i9dvf80hk764lb", "type": "i_answer"}, {"uid": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "anon": "no", "when": "2015-05-07T07:48:12Z", "data": "i9dvgheencp3x0", "type": "i_answer_update"}, {"uid": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "anon": "no", "when": "2015-05-07T07:49:03Z", "data": "i9dvhkvbjum43i", "type": "i_answer_update"}], "bucket_name": "Today", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "i6roqnlkmtw", "subject": "关于lock_mm的用处", "created": "2015-05-07T07:17:45Z", "content": "<p>lab7里面为每个mm_struct增加了一个信号量</p>\n<pre>struct mm_struct {\n    list_entry_t mmap_list;        // linear list link which sorted by start addr of vma\n    struct vma_struct *mmap_cache; // current accessed vma, used for speed purpose\n    pde_t *pgdir;                  // the PDT of these vma\n    int map_count;                 // the count of these vma\n    void *sm_priv;                 // the private data for swap manager\n    int mm_count;                  // the number ofprocess which shared the mm\n    semaphore_t mm_sem;            // mutex for using dup_mmap fun to duplicat the mm \n    int locked_by;                 // the lock owner process&#39;s pid\n};</pre>\n<p>然后有两个操作lock_mm和unlock_mm可以用来保证同一时间只有一个进程能够访问某个mm_struct</p>\n<p>我查到的唯一一个用到lock_mm的地方是在</p>\n<p>process/proc.c的copy_mm里面&#xff0c;创建新进程的时候拷贝原有进程的mm_struct&#xff0c;然后在dup_mmap前后内存加锁了</p>\n<pre>    lock_mm(oldmm);\n    {\n        ret = dup_mmap(mm, oldmm);\n    }\n    unlock_mm(oldmm);</pre>\n<p>我不太理解这样做的意义何在啊&#xff1f;</p>\n<p>dup_mmap读取原有oldmm中的内容&#xff0c;写到新的mm里面去&#xff0c;是对原有oldmm的一个只读操作&#xff0c;为什么要加锁呢&#xff1f;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>"}], "type": "question", "tags": ["lab7", "student"], "tag_good": [], "unique_views": 82, "children": [{"folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "children": [], "created": "2015-05-07T07:41:15Z", "bucket_order": 3, "tag_endorse": [{"role": "", "name": "Ruidong CAO", "endorser": {}, "admin": false, "photo": null, "id": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "photo_url": null, "us": false, "class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "清华学生_i5j09fnsl7k5x0", "所有老师和助教_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "facebook_id": null}], "bucket_name": "Today", "id": "i9dv7k3vrzric", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "hxu22d7okof4c1", "subject": "", "created": "2015-05-07T07:41:15Z", "content": "<p>lock_mm(oldmm)是为了防止边复制oldmm边被修改。现在看起来只有一处lock_mm&#xff0c;当然没有用&#xff0c;但到lab8里面就好多地方用lock_mm了。</p>"}], "type": "s_answer", "tag_endorse_arr": ["hs2swpdtr91gu"], "config": {}, "is_tag_endorse": false}, {"folders": [], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "children": [], "created": "2015-05-07T07:47:13Z", "bucket_order": 3, "tag_endorse": [], "bucket_name": "Today", "id": "i9dvf80ff3a4la", "history": [{"anon": "no", "uid": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "subject": "", "created": "2015-05-07T07:49:03Z", "content": "<p></p>"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "subject": "", "created": "2015-05-07T07:48:12Z", "content": "<p></p>"}, {"anon": "no", "uid": "hs2swpdtr91gu", "subject": "", "created": "2015-05-07T07:47:13Z", "content": "<p>在lab8中会有更多的函数调用lock_mm&#xff0c;在这里加锁是有必要的&#xff0c;防止读取的内容被修改</p>"}], "type": "i_answer", "tag_endorse_arr": [], "config": {}, "is_tag_endorse": false}], "tag_good_arr": [], "no_answer": 0, "id": "i9dudbt5alg262", "config": {}, "status": "active", "drafts": null, "request_instructor": 0, "request_instructor_me": false, "bookmarked": 4, "num_favorites": 0, "my_favorite": false, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "q_edits": [], "i_edits": [], "s_edits": [], "t": 1643167736634, "default_anonymity": "no"}, "error": null, "aid": "kyuzn7zuiud3hy"